ABOUT
Project EVO is the �rst mobile survival game developed with Unreal Engine 5. It
will be released in 2023. THE WORLD HAS BEEN RUINED. RAID FOR EMBERS,
FIGHT FOR SURVIVAL! In this open world known as Emberland, the only aim is to
survive... till the very end. Danger lurks around every corner, everything wants
you dead. You have to survive through the cruelest of competition - not only
against all kinds of mutant creatures, but against hundreds of other desperate
players. Keep in mind, by hook or by crook, everything goes! But being alive is
always the aim of the game. The light of Ember is guiding your way. Embark on
this fantastic journey, NOW!

Gameplay Updates:
�. Canceled the limit that players could join up to only 3 new Sessions per
day. Now, each player can have up to 7 in-progress Sessions at a time.
�. Optimized the Lobby Squad system to help players �nd a Squad earlier on.
�. Optimized how the Airdrop mechanic worked in Sessions as well as its
rewards, spawn rates, and VFX.
�. Optimized PvE rewards. Adjusted the number of Supplies that Zombies
drop.
�. Optimized the PvP combat stats. Adjusted weapon DMG and armor DEF.
�. Optimized how Territory was repaired while in combat. The new mechanic
is: While in combat, repairing your Territory Structure takes a while to
complete. During that time, if the Structure comes under attack, the repair
fails; if not, it gets repaired.
�. Updated the Ember mechanic:
�. Canceled the mechanic that players could use Embers to level up
their Territory and increase the capacity of their Safe.
�. Embers are now consumables. Players can keep them in their Ember
Chest to yield Ember Energy and Ember Points. Ember Energy will
determine your ranking on the leaderboard. And you can spend
Ember Points to redeem certain Supplies.
�. Canceled the leaderboard daily rewards.
�. Added Ember Point rewards. The content and number of Supply
rewards now refresh daily2. Fixed the issue that sometimes the
e�ects of a piece of armor became di�erent once it was equipped to
a character from the Backpack.
